{"tid":472081,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大學/大專既gp project 都係多如","createTime":"2017-11-18T01:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T06:13:08.000Z","uid":158738,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff88f03758fcb91b18d8c571f49ad86d14965c9","tid":472081,"uid":158738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:03:42.000Z","msg":"見到有po 問present 有乜用，呢樣野都尚可爭論。但毫無疑問gp project 真係多鳩如，project 根本唔可以體現團隊精神，真正落手落腳去chur 既都係得一兩個人，其他人一定係懶理，一係就等到deadline 前兩三日先問進度，一係直頭free ride 你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能有人會話咁人都有強弱既地方，group project 分工都係互補長短，但其實我覺得group project 只係一個多字版既individual assignment, 如果你做到一份individual, 咁做group project其實你有時間既話一定可以自己砌一份出黎，如果你有足夠時間都做唔到既話，其實上到大學你真係會辛苦。<br />\n雖然free rider 係可以port, 但又要有足夠證據證明佢真係free ride 先鋤得入。<br />\n希望喺我有生之年見到所有大學/大專取消group project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8a8cd88f40504066b267a25bcb878cf0cfe425","tid":472081,"uid":158738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0108862cae469686c611cf0056d1fb2624ee28ea","tid":472081,"uid":40779,"like":10,"dislike":12,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:09:55.000Z","msg":"group project係用泥揾女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77fcb30fff702fb08381567617a98b7f38e48eb","tid":472081,"uid":1152,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:12:36.000Z","msg":"多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e65f56a37bdfa5dd3adff9a90d4d2a2e57daf26","tid":472081,"uid":1152,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>group project係用泥揾女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泥你老母"},{"pid":"98ddea9797f79559e2fdc1374a54ee48e112d976","tid":472081,"uid":158738